      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "和尚洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你就说我宁可去陪母狗吃屎，也不愿再见她，再喝她的牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好好的一个人，为什么偏偏要去陪母狗吃屎呢？",
