      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我偷偷的藏起了一条小船，所以她就认为你们一定是坐船跑了，否则他们怎么会找不到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就因为找不到你们，这两天九少爷和宫主的脾气都大得要命，幸好他们做梦也想不到这些事是谁做的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "究竟是谁做的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "除了我还有谁？",
