      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不饿，就算饿也不吃。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "原来曼姑娘真的是在吃醋，原来吃醋也能吃得饱的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她不吃我吃。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚几时开始吃荤的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "饿疯了的时候。",
